air:Brand.air:Title: Economy
ECONOMY
air:Brand.air:Text:
Our lowest available fare with options to customize travel and without the restrictions of Budget Economy.
Benefits include: - Seat selection at booking, if seats are available - Eligible to change ticket. - Eligible to request a same-day change. - Carry on bag • Please note that if the flight is operated by another airline then the onboard product or service maybe different to that described above.
